{"tid":1683830,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"80m追隻契弟小醜，真係獌狗先做到","createTime":"2019-10-30T21:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:50:23.000Z","uid":555,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe58ab39f617fee77886e1e1562728dda8d95ac","tid":1683830,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:26:57.000Z","msg":"睇住呢種柒真係令人心頭一振<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上季想買人，嫌貴無買到，已經柒一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n季尾幾條廢鳩連横自爆，又柒一鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果迫住唔屌又屌80m高追隻英格蘭狗，柒第三獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見班獌狗早兩個禮拜 J到天昏地暗，以為咩球王君臨咁巴閉啦，屌你老母一睇，嘩，水撚到吖，我以為睇緊學界啊80m 鐵衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一隊波可以由上至下都柒到咁勻循、咁立體、咁不堪入目，仲要自以為係一線班霸，世上真係得一隊臭獌狗做得到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e3b148d49929915d68445e8d2f2bf2328a9644","tid":1683830,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:29:06.000Z","msg":"雲迪克夠失五球啦"},{"pid":"5b8a7ab403abd8d5dbf1c2205d9684b9351129bc","tid":1683830,"uid":72751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b8e3b148d49929915d68445e8d2f2bf2328a9644","tid":1683830,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:29:06.000Z","msg":"雲迪克夠失五球啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:49:28.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"5c9f671ff531c1df3a77ecb1a8226eb42ebbcbeb","tid":1683830,"uid":218179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8e3b148d49929915d68445e8d2f2bf2328a9644","tid":1683830,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:29:06.000Z","msg":"雲迪克夠失五球啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:50:43.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"a6a7d253b6c896fbb0a1c62ce16e737421aa6c0e","tid":1683830,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8e3b148d49929915d68445e8d2f2bf2328a9644","tid":1683830,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:29:06.000Z","msg":"雲迪克夠失五球啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T22:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0fd2ae34f20f30596372651c1e85f443fe60fe","tid":1683830,"uid":92465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":